data.description: Welcome to your perfect home near the Atlanta airport, offering peace and tranquility for families, professionals, and college students alike (near Clayton State University) Situated just 30 minutes from Downtown Atlanta and a short 15-minute drive from Stockbridge, this location provides the ideal balance between convenience and serenity. Prepare to embrace the future with our Smart Home features. Imagine the ease and comfort of controlling your home and garage's functions & packages with just a few taps on your phone. However, rest assured that this home is available on a first-come, first-serve basis. This modern home, built in 2018, offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a generous 2,374 square feet of living space; you'll enjoy a range of amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle. Stay comfortable year-round with the included 2 zoned HVAC system, and indulge in the elegance of GRANITE open kitchen countertops and MARBLE bathroom countertops. LAUNDRY will be a breeze with the provided washer and dryer. Step into a home equipped with brand new appliances, including a smart washer, dryer, refrigerator, dishwasher, and a 2-car garage. The extra-large primary bedroom suite offers a peaceful retreat, while the upgraded dining room area is perfect for entertaining guests and creating lasting memories. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this house your home. Contact today for more information and to schedule a viewing in this desirable Atlanta neighborhood, close to the airport and ready to welcome you with open arms. This home is located in sought after Legacy At Stagecoach Swim/Tennis Community. Tons of natural light home awaits you!
